hints.description: Assuming that today is the 30th June 2020, can you tell me the last day I was changing a plug on an electrical device?
How many times did I visit an outdoor/farmers market in February 2020?
At what time did I go to the cafe in TheHelix on that day in January 2020, after returning from my trip to MMM and to Bangkok?
On which date in March 2019 did the cafeteria offer a sweet potato, coconut & chili soup? That was really tasty.
I live near the sea. Find examples of when I was taking a photo of the sea with my smartphone.
Find examples of when I was wearing my red Vietnam football shirt.

I try to eat healthy, but sometimes I fail. Find examples of when I was eating fast food (e.g. Mc Donalds, Burger King, Lotteria), Eating in a normal (not-fast food) restaurant is not considered relevant. Ordering food (before eating) is not considered relevant.

I remember a really ugly house for sale. Find examples of this house-for-sale with a visible ‘for-sale’ sign outside and with trees beside and behind the house. The for sale sign was orange and blue I think.
